               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence</hi>. A gentleman asked me if I wanted to earn a shil<lb></lb>ling—he put this on my shoulder—I went across—the prosecutor came and seized me, and said it was his—I gave it him without hesitation—the crowd and round, and I do not know what became of the gentleman.</p>
